charging operation, which kept both boilers running above 50% load. \n\t\n\tAll in all good voyage."},{"modifiedDate":"2021-09-22T15:04:34.983","modifiedByFull":"Masembo, Miguel","remark":"Chtrs exercised the option of loading earlier than commencement of laydays - Per Cl 12 - Charterers shall have the benefit of such time saved by way of offset from any demurrage incured.\nSuch benefit shall be the time between commencement of loading until the commencement of the original laydays."},{"modifiedDate":"2021-09-22T14:59:57.1","modifiedByFull":"Masembo, Miguel","remark":"Flat rate revised basis loading port  Angra dos Reis, TEBIG Terminal - 13.37"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}